41:05.596 --> 41:06.696
Okay.

41:06.698 --> 41:08.231
â™ª

41:08.233 --> 41:10.633
I'm in. Let's do it.

41:10.635 --> 41:14.938
â™ª

41:14.940 --> 41:18.174
Take it easy.
I know. I know.

41:18.176 --> 41:19.175
Nice.
(wheels and lever clack)

41:19.177 --> 41:24.948
The pathology report for
your sentinel node dissection...

41:24.950 --> 41:28.618
Negative.
Mom, that's great.
It is, right?

41:28.620 --> 41:32.088
It means I'm gonna be around
for a while.
Good. (chuckles)

41:32.090 --> 41:34.724
I thought you might want
to go over my pitch

41:34.726 --> 41:36.826
To the tumor board
for staging of chemo.

41:36.828 --> 41:39.796
No. I trust my doctor.

41:39.798 --> 41:43.800
We can go over it tomorrow.
No, no. Don't go.
Don't go.

41:43.802 --> 41:45.635
Stay, it's about to start.

41:45.637 --> 41:48.671
Sorry, I'm late. Popcorn.
Ooh.

41:48.673 --> 41:51.941
I snuck this past
the nurses' station.
(chuckles)

41:51.943 --> 41:53.576
It's a party.

41:53.578 --> 41:55.612
(molly) come on!
Come on!

41:55.614 --> 41:57.113
Come on.
Oh, what the hell.

41:57.115 --> 41:59.549
(laughter)

41:59.551 --> 42:00.850
(molly) it's starting,
it's starting, it's starting.
(dana) oh.

42:00.852 --> 42:01.985
<i>â™ª</i>

42:01.987 --> 42:04.087
(emilia) gimme some of that.

42:04.089 --> 42:07.257
Oh, I love it already.
(mouth full) me, too.

42:08.959 --> 42:10.793
Okay, they're gonna let
the audience in, in a second,

42:10.795 --> 42:13.696
But before they do,
I wanted to share

42:13.698 --> 42:16.866
A message with you from
your teacher--miss paulina--

42:16.868 --> 42:19.936
Who, unfortunately,
couldn't be with us tonight.

42:19.938 --> 42:22.805
Um, and she said,

42:22.807 --> 42:25.275
"tonight...

42:25.277 --> 42:30.113
"you are the keepers
of your own pixie dust.

42:30.115 --> 42:32.815
"so carry it with you.

42:32.817 --> 42:35.552
"and remember
our little secret.

42:35.554 --> 42:39.322
"every night is opening night,

42:39.324 --> 42:41.758
"and every step you take
is magic.

42:41.760 --> 42:43.793
So carry that in your hearts."

42:43.795 --> 42:45.728
Oh, and--
and who's colleen?

42:45.730 --> 42:47.964
Um...

42:47.966 --> 42:52.569
Keep your toe out.

42:52.571 --> 42:56.839
Anyway, one... Two...

42:56.841 --> 42:58.841
Three! Yay!
(girls) yay!

42:58.843 --> 43:00.743
Okay, places, everybody.
Places!

43:00.745 --> 43:03.212
(girls giggling)

